## Handoff Receiving Template

```
=== PERPLEXITY HANDOFF PACKAGE ===
Project: [name]
Handed off from: [platform] ([phase])
Receiving: Perplexity (research phase)

[If using a Space: open the relevant Space before pasting]

Research brief:

Context: [2-sentence description of the project and why this research matters]

What we already know:
- [Finding 1 already established — don't re-research this]
- [Finding 2]

What I need you to research:
1. [Specific research question 1]
2. [Specific research question 2]
3. [Specific research question 3]

Source requirements:
- [e.g., "Focus on sources from the last 6 months"]
- [e.g., "Include analyst reports and primary sources where available"]
- [e.g., "Prioritize primary sources over aggregators"]

Output format:
- Findings organized by question
- Each finding linked to its source
- Flag any conflicting information across sources
- Note confidence level where sources are thin

Re-entry: When complete, copy the full research output.
Run: /handoff return from Perplexity
This will be synthesized and incorporated into [destination: Claude / document / etc.]

=== END ===
```

## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] Use Pro Search for complex multi-source queries
- [ ] Open or create a Space if this is part of ongoing research
- [ ] Specify recency requirements in the prompt if current data matters
- [ ] Break complex research tasks into 2–3 focused queries rather than one broad one
- [ ] Save key findings to the Space before handing back
